      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WALTER WANTED (3) goes very well this course and distance starting 15 times for six wins and five minors. Placed last time (23.51) at Dubbo in a Grade 5, finishing second and beaten a nose. Expected to be in the finish. MAYBE YES (5) finished in the money fresh when third (20.04) at this track in a Grade 4/5. Has a good record here including five wins. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from four starts. Will give a great sight again. TIPSY ETHICS (1) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fourth (18.84) in a Grade 4/5 at Dubbo. Solid record here winning two races. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and five minor placings to her credit. In the mix. JAMAICA RUM (2) will have admirers after surprising many with a placing last time out.",
